${font Ubuntu:size=8}${voffset -67}${color3}${goto 108}${freq_g (1)}GHz ${goto 258}${freq_g (2)}GHz ${goto 0}${voffset 50}${goto 108}${freq_g (3)}GHz ${goto 258}${freq_g (4)}GHz 
